actions.message:
Hello, ${member}

If you're able to use this command, it means you're authorized to use the following commands.

The prefix for the bot is `.`

.start - Will start all the servers, 1 through 5 with 10 second intervals between all 5.
.endall - WIll kill all the server, 1 through 5.
.end1 - Will kill server 1.
.end2 - Will kill server 2.
.end3 - Will kill server 3.
.end4 - Will kill server 4.
.end5 - Will kill server 5.
.who - Displays who made me.
.help Displays this message.
